author: Jeff Cox
description: Markets will be watching intently for which Trump boards Air Force One to take a sojourn across the Middle East.
title: A market 'starting to give up' is watching Trump's foreign trip closely

author: Edwin Mora
description: The U.S. Air Force considers “maintaining space superiority” one of its "core missions," warning that “space is now a warfighting domain.”
title: U.S. Military Warns 'Space Is Now a Warfighting Domain' - Breitbart

author: Jeff Daniels
description: Staying one step ahead of bad guys is one of the reasons the Air Force is now inviting hackers to join an upcoming bug bounty challenge.
title: Air Force seeking hackers as military prepares for its largest bug bounty program yet

author: Joel B. Pollak
description: The New York Times waited until Trump was aloft on Air Force One before reporting that he told the Russians James Comey was a "nut job."
title: 'Nut Job': New York Times Collaborates with Deep State to Smear Trump Again - Breitbart

description: Donald Trump set off on Air Force One for Saudi Arabia for the start of his first international trip as president, with the kingdom rolling out the red carpet and preparing to serve his favourite meal of steak and ketchup.
title: Saudi Arabia to offer Donald Trump steak and ketchup on first presidential trip abroad

description: Two Chinese fighter jets conducted an “unprofessional” intercept of a US Air Force plane, US officials said, with one flying upside down directly above the aircraft in a manoeuvre similar to the one performed in the Hollywood movie Top Gun.
title: US blasts China over 'unprofessional' intercept of military plane by fighter jets

author: Alle Beiträge von dpa  anzeigen.
description: Die Air Force One mit Präsident Donald Trump hat gerade Richtung Saudi Arabien abgehoben, da werden neue Vorwürfe laut. Ein enger Mitarbeiter soll zudem in den Fokus der Ermittlungen gerückt sein.
title: Neue „Person von Interesse“: Russland-Ermittlungen ausgeweitet
